                                                  ASSIGNMENT FILE I/O
												  
Q1 Write a Python program to read an entire text file.
 
Q2  Write a Python program to append text to a file and display the text.

Q3 Write a Python program to read a file line by line and store it into a list.

Q4Write a python program to find the longest words.

Q5 Write a Python program to combine each line from first file with the corresponding line in second file.

Q6 Find the average of each line from the file and display it seperately in a dictionary.
Expected output:
Average of no in lines
{('average of line', 1): 442.4, ('average of line', 2): 481.8}

Q7 Find the average of each year seperately and show it seperately yearwise in a dictionary.
Expected output:
{('average of year', 1992): 55.0, ('average of year', 2001): 102.0}

Q8 Write a Python program to get the file size of a plain file.

Q9 Write a Python program to write a list to a file.

Q10 Write a Python program to remove newline characters from a file. 